      • REPUBLISH_UNACKED_MESSAGES

        public static final int REPUBLISH_UNACKED_MESSAGES
        After successfully reconnecting a disconnected session, the SDK received an unknown publisher flow name response when reconnecting the GD publisher flow. If configured to auto-retry ( SessionHandle.PROPERTIES.GD_RECONNECT_FAIL_ACTION is GdReconnectFailAction.AUTO_RETRY ) this event is generated to indicate how many unacknowledged messages are retransmitted on success. As the publisher state has been lost on failover, receiving this event may indicate that some messages have been duplicated in the system.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
